		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />PCB class: Nintendo HVC-SXROM-01<br />U1 PRG-ROM: ATH-87-0 PRG, 0x20000 byte ROM, CRC32: 0xd1e50064<br />U2 CHR-RAM: LH5168FB-10L, 0x2000 byte RAM<br />U4 W-RAM: LH52A256-10LL, 0x8000 byte RAM (banked)<br /><br />high resolution and other sides scan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www1.axfc.net/u/3179252.zip">http://www1.axfc.net/u/3179252.zip</a><!-- m --><br /><br />nescartdb にはどうやって登録するの?

		
