		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A third SXROM game ? Cool, I always tought there were only 2.<br /><br />Does it use all 32k of SRAM ?<br />As far I know both Final Fantasy I &amp; II and Best Play Pro Yakyuu Special used only 16k (both are multicard with 2 games on them I think, please tell me if I'm wrong).

		

